text.__SUMMARY__: Prunus rubiginosa is a species of plant in the family Rosaceae. It is endemic to the Philippines.
text.Sources: Kalkman, C. (1998). "Prunus rubiginosa". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T37391A10044282. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T37391A10044282.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
